by Ololo and friends?!
Littlepon worried?!?!

single word Dad say, but
secretly still worry...

wonderful daughterpon...

rows.label: qst640405_msg0105

in plant all done now, so Gisisi
head back home quick-quick.

rows.label: qst640405_msg0106

Sky-Jewel Tart that me buy as gift.

rows.label: qst640405_msg0107

Feeling of loving family is
hotter that any hot spring...
